description:
Safe, clean, professionally managed property awaits your next stay! Massachusetts urges all out of state visitors to self quarantine for 14 days.

Cleanliness: Before you arrive, our cleaning staff have used a disinfectant to wipe down your entire room, bathroom and kitchen counter tops, sinks, handles & toilets.

For all locals & stays 7+ nights, a copy of your license and proof of work in town is required within 24 hours of booking.

Bathroom NOT private to the room!*

The space
Bay Village Suites is happy to offer 36 high-efficiency rooms with shared bathrooms. All rooms are furnished with high-quality furniture and modern amenities, designed for the modern traveler. The room is furnished with a queen size memory foam bed, TV for streaming, high-speed internet with wifi connectivity, a desk, and storage space. The kitchen has a efficiency size refrigerator, toaster, microwave, and coffee pot.
